<b> use css custom property , variables for colors/ theme</b>

font-style: try using apple-system.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

On hover box shadow:
:hover {
    border: 1px solid #fa7328;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgb(0 0 0 / 20%), 0 1px 10px rgb(0 0 0 / 12%), 0 4px 5px rgb(0 0 0 / 14%);
    or
    box-shadow: 0 8px 12px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2)
}

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  -webkit-transition: 0.3s;
  transition: 0.3s;
 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
  font-size: 15-20px
  

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
* {
padding: 0;
margin: 0;
max-width: 100%;
overflow-x: hidden;
position: relative;
display: block;
}

